  "bib_entries": {
    "194966955": {
      "title": "Cowboy Culture: A Saga of Five Centuries",
      "abstract": "A nationwide bestseller with more than 65,000 copies in print since publication by Alfred A. Knopf in 1981, this fascinating chronicle of cowboy life and legend is now available in a trade paperback edition. It's the 500-year saga of the \"real cowboy\" from fifteenth-century Mexico to the twentieth-century American West.\""
